name: Genesis Art by Belle on HEN
description:
My genesis piece on Hen. I’m Belle, an emerging artist and a member of the community. I look forward to making connections on a deeper level beyond just being fellow nft members with everyone out here. I don’t know my way around here but I sure do know I can’t wait to meet you so here goes nothing probably:
 Hello Fam👋🏽 I hope you resonate with my work and i look forward to feedbacks from every person regardless of your identity. I hope you like🙏🏽
I
